{
  "stem": "10960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I took that-- that-- that sack, you know, from the empty bags, and I put it in like this, all the way, inside, like you-- you-- you pulled up your-- your stocking.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All the way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I crawled into that barrel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Near me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I took back, covered back myself with the same wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Like wood trees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Not cutted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The heavy [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Near me was the stepladder to the roof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When they broke the doors, they were thinking that I went-- I saw them, but they didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They were there, there, there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The-- the Ukrainians were-- were giving them instructions, maybe there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But they saw me running in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But they didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they walked away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there was a wind, and that day was, that evening was, a terrible wind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The doors opened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "All of a sudden, when I-- as I was sitting there, I hear that-- like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the wind-- and the wind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and the Ukraine were came in, and they throw it out, through the windows, things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "A lot of-- all the things, which-- belongings from my sister's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I thought to myself, I'll wait up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In a wind like this, it's good to run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They won't to hear me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this is what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I waited up, and I didn't hear any shooting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because otherwise, from the beginning on, as they were, you know, pushing the people to the trucks, there-- there was different.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But as-- as it quiet down, the went quiet down, so I took myself out slowly from that barrel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I crawled in back to the place, I thought to myself, here I'll see maybe my-- my baby is still alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I only saw the blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I didn't see no more of my baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
